Package builder

Class MotorcycleBuilder

java.lang.Object
builder.MotorcycleBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
VehicleBuilder
public class MotorcycleBuilder extends Object implements VehicleBuilder
Concrete builder for creating Motorcycle instances. Implements the VehicleBuilder interface for step-by-step construction of a motorcycle.
